      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and is drivable, but shows noticeable wear both inside and out. The exterior has visible scratches and some fading paint. The interior surfaces are worn, and there are minor mechanical issues that should be addressed. Suitable for a buyer looking for basic transportation at a lower price point.",
